{"tid":1425241,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你入嚟，我話你知勇武派嘅真正用處！","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:35:19.000Z","uid":110857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2cbe502d76ea8b80abed6550e07470cd468968","tid":1425241,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"到咗今時今日，無論你支唔支持勇武派嘅行動都好，我可以話你知，每次出現狗仔隊嘅地方，都會有一大堆市民自發出現。<br />\n<br />\n呢一點好重要！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當越多人真正感受到狗嘅無理，社會就會出現更強烈嘅輿論壓力。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做到呢一樣，威力比係facebook做文宣同做民間press con都嚟得更有效率更大力！<br />\n<br />\n係時候全民出動，令仲選擇做狗嘅人真正受到無比嘅壓力！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">越多人屌，壓力就越大</span></span>！你估下究竟有幾多人心中可以強大到比主流意見怒屌都唔崩壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，係保護到街坊嘅同時，又可以令佢地親身體驗狗嘅不公。可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為，呢個絕對可以係一個好方向！"},{"pid":"5cbcfcd6dfd0a1fcceb6cc4e615269b32eaf7583","tid":1425241,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca05300b1e65c821b9c0fe401428593427ee7ee0","tid":1425241,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:33:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a330cc8e5d206ada159b4e7906580a6bf194af6a","tid":1425241,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:33:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1559b07d68de07849791296102919fad627632ec","tid":1425241,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:34:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7cbef6c3b3ac618d90dbe93a37de4cfdbbfcdf5a","tid":1425241,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"1"}]}